<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />Purify me with hyssop, and I will be clean;</para>

<para style="q1">wash me, and I will be whiter than snow.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Make me hear joy and gladness</para>

<para style="q1">so that the bones that you have broken may rejoice.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Hide your face from my sins</para>

<para style="q1">and blot out all my iniquities.</para>
